{"questionId":"7444","questionHtml":"<p>A ball of mass <em>m</em> collides with a wall and bounces back in a straight line. The ball loses 75 % of&nbsp;the initial energy during the collision. The speed before the collision is <em>v</em>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"__IMG__/32752a423feacfafc437a3404f8aa423975ea7f3.png\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">What is the magnitude of the impulse on the ball by the wall?</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">A.&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {1 - \\frac{{\\sqrt 3 }}{2}} \\right)mv\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mfrac>\n        <mrow>\n          <msqrt>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </msqrt>\n        </mrow>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n      </mfrac>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mi>m</mi>\n  <mi>v</mi>\n</math></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">B.&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{1}{2}mv\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mn>1</mn>\n    <mn>2</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mi>m</mi>\n  <mi>v</mi>\n</math></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">C.&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{5}{4}mv\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mn>5</mn>\n    <mn>4</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mi>m</mi>\n  <mi>v</mi>\n</math></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">D.&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{3}{2}mv\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mn>3</mn>\n    <mn>2</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mi>m</mi>\n  <mi>v</mi>\n</math></span></p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>D</p>","meta":{"questionId":"7444","referenceCode":"18N.1.SL.TZ0.9","subjectId":"46-dp-physics-last-assessment-2024","title":"A ball of mass m collides with a wall and bounces back in a straight line. The ball loses 75 % of the initial energy during the collision. The speed before the collision is v. What","paper":"1","level":"SL","questionNumber":"9","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Core","Core","Topic 2: Mechanics","2.4 – Momentum and impulse","Core","Topic 2: Mechanics"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}